headers.subject: [tosdr:1965] Tumblr will notify you of price changes

html:
Tumblr may change its prices for Paid Services at any time. To the extent applicable, Tumblr will provide you reasonable notice of any such pricing changes by posting the new prices on or through the applicable Paid Service and/or by sending you email notification. If you do not wish to pay the new prices, you may choose not to purchase, or to cancel, the applicable Paid Service prior to the change going into effect.

http://www.tumblr.com/policy/en/terms_of_service 

--
